title: Don't keep two similar tables in the same .org file.
pid: a90bc443-c736-4e76-ac3b-348708f57cbc
body: |2-
  Rather, keep two hyperlinks in it, to two more separate files.
  Otherwise, when searching for one table,
  I'll often find and edit the other, which sucks.
